Re: ニンテンド(Nintendo)!!!
by furrykef » Sun 11.29.2009 10:22 am I don't really care one way or the other about their gaming consoles or the games for them, but as a game developer, I wish their development kits were better. I can't go into further details, though, 'cause I'm under a nondisclosure agreement.I remember when I was a kid (well... in many ways I still am one) and I wondered what it'd be like to develop games for Nintendo systems. Now that I know, I kinda wish I didn't know. OK, here's one thing about Nintendo that I'd change: bring back the SNES! Seriously. I'm a diehard retrogamer, so the SNES basically represents all that's good about gaming to me. (And in a year the damn thing will have its 20th birthday.)- Kef
